title: The Pallbearer (1996) David Schwimmer Gwyneth Paltrow
description:
www.imdb.com/title/tt0117283/

David Schwimmer from 'Friends' in one of his funniest feature films, according to my taste:
A young man's life is thrown into a loop when he is asked to be a pallbearer for the funeral of a classmate he doesn't remember.

Widescreen, good stereo.
Burn tested, runs well in my DivX player.
